{"type":"text","timestamp":1775842651275,"sessionID":"ses_2878842d6ffez9StiW3AWeNYRZ","part":{"id":"prt_d787846a80015hfuraSMA9MPr1","messageID":"msg_d78783cf8001cxTgD6lj5m6P62","sessionID":"ses_2878842d6ffez9StiW3AWeNYRZ","type":"text","text":"## AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 Archive\n\n### Completed\n\n**Core HTTP Server Framework:**\n- `server.go` - Gin server setup with graceful shutdown, Kubernetes dynamic client initialization\n- `config.go` - Configuration loading from environment variables (PORT, KUBECONFIG, NAMESPACE, RESYNC_PERIOD, DEBUG)\n- `routes.go` - Route registration for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter endpoints with middleware stack\n\n**Handlers:**\n- `handler/agent_runtime.go` - Full CRUD for AgentRuntime (Create/List/Get/Update/Delete)\n- `handler/code_interpreter.go` - Full CRUD for CodeInterpreter (Create/List/Get/Update/Delete)\n- `handler/health.go` - Health check endpoints (`/healthz`, `/readyz`)\n\n**Infrastructure:**\n- `middleware/request_id.go` - Request ID tracing middleware\n- `response/response.go` - Standardized response formatting\n\n**Tests:**\n- All handlers have corresponding `*_test.go` files\n- `server_test.go`, `routes_test.go`, `config_test.go`\n\n**API Endpoints Implemented:**\n- `GET /healthz`, `GET /readyz`\n- `POST/GET/PUT/DELETE /api/v1/agentruntimes[/:name]`\n- `POST/GET/PUT/DELETE /api/v1/codeinterpreters[/:name]`\n\n---\n\n### Deferred\n\n**Per design.md (1135 lines), the following were NOT implemented:**\n\n**Service Layer:**\n- `service.go` - WorkloadManager interface (abstracted service layer)\n- `client.go` - Separate client initialization file\n\n**Missing Middleware:**\n- `middleware/auth.go` - JWT/Kubernetes TokenReview authentication\n- `middleware/logging.go` - Request logging middleware\n- `middleware/error.go` - Centralized error handling middleware\n\n**Missing Features:**\n- Informer-based caching (uses direct dynamic client calls instead)\n- Prometheus metrics endpoint (`/metrics`)\n- Pagination support for list operations\n- Label/Field selector filtering\n- Status update endpoints (`PATCH /api/v1/agentruntimes/{name}/status`)\n- Redis-backed store integration\n- CORS middleware\n\n**API Gaps:**\n- No pagination query params (`page`, `pageSize`)\n- No `labelSelector`/`fieldSelector` support\n- No subresource status updates\n\n**Test Coverage:**\n- Integration tests (`integration_test.go`)\n- Mock infrastructure (`mocks_test.go`)\n- Middleware tests (auth, logging, error handling)","time":{"start":1775842651273,"end":1775842651273}}}
